Description: Provides tools for performing Feature-based Metabolite Set Enrichment 
    Analysis (fMSEA). This package integrates isotopic peak annotation and 
    metabolite set prediction directly from mass spectrometry feature data, 
    supporting complex adduct and isotope matching logic.
